messages.speech: I was carrying, files, and two laptops, or two bags and what happened is that it was a meeting. It was a very important meeting with representatives from 153 different countries, and we were inside the meeting room and it's long, long, long, long tables with chairs on each side. And I was staggering through the chairs, and what happened is that I was holding the coffee, and then my bag fell from my shoulder to my elbow. And the coffee just went like Vhoo inside the meeting room, and it landed on the representative from India and ...
